{"tid":720161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【博物古蹟】有冇人去咗大館 (舊中區警署) 參觀?","createTime":"2018-06-27T17:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T10:26:33.000Z","uid":24160,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9a937bb817df24049c7206488bd2b1205f142f83","tid":720161,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:20:15.000Z","msg":"上個月底開放畀公眾免費參觀嘅舊區警署<br />\n點解好似冇連登仔講嘅?<br />\n<br />\n我都係睇天后fb先得知開放咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入面已經翻新到好靚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n活化後的警察總部大樓和檢閱廣場（2018年）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011057_00a78098bef38c0a2d2e5665af955770.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011057_00a78098bef38c0a2d2e5665af955770.png&h=f32ccead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活化後監獄外的通道（2018年）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011059_31a4b469ecf7b623596adbea432a73ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011059_31a4b469ecf7b623596adbea432a73ff.png&h=6db03886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活化後的監獄內貌，圖為B倉（域多利鐵窗生涯）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011100_3c1bd0ae17e7678a287a3a573fceec77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011100_3c1bd0ae17e7678a287a3a573fceec77.png&h=94f70a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個好似蘭花劫嗰時個廣場???<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011101_bb931726ca9e346d35c1d16f405cae06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011101_bb931726ca9e346d35c1d16f405cae06.png&h=b8169caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白雪雪好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011212_93a9b174ee308844345c79d4eb2e612e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011212_93a9b174ee308844345c79d4eb2e612e.png&h=c15c829f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011945_8373a0d7d56a09f051276ecab9526448.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011945_8373a0d7d56a09f051276ecab9526448.png&h=81d71378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011213_f1cec30a5a0fc10610a11bb85a187302.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011213_f1cec30a5a0fc10610a11bb85a187302.png&h=e43c757a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011216_a48731972590ea3f03674267b20ee280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011216_a48731972590ea3f03674267b20ee280.png&h=a83d76e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011218_80ec498b78a46e5ecc66d09fba14508e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F011218_80ec498b78a46e5ecc66d09fba14508e.png&h=a35ec720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/011219_8667074eaa7a7